    public class BaseDialogFragment
extends DialogFragment
    Package: com.paulmender.udacity.popularmovies.app Project: PopularMovies Stage 2 Name: BaseMovieDialogFragment Purpose: Base class for dialog fragments. Create a parameter bundle using the BUNDLE_KEY_* constants as needed, then setArgument(the parameter bundle). Author: Paul on 20180128. References: 1. https://developer.android.com/guide/topics/ui/dialogs.html 2. https://developer.android.com/reference/android/app/DialogFragment.html
